    "description": "Auto Server Co., Ltd. provides internet based used car distribution services in Japan. The company operates ASNET, a car distribution platform that offers web based services, including auction agency services, such as bidding, POS push bids, price negotiations, and other related services; brokering trade sales of instore inventory; and retail support services, as well as e commerce services. It is also involved in buying and listing cars; car part sales; and convenient services comprising direct search, market price information, automatic land transport arrangement, e mail service, English mode, auto loans, and used car warranties. In addition, the company plans, develops, sells, and maintains computer systems. It serves automobile sales, auto maintenance, auto parts suppliers, and gas station industries. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
